message: "If you use or build on this work, please cite it as below. The FEGA MWG membership list is maintained in AUTHORS.md (source of truth)."
title: "EGA Metadata Schemas"
version: 2.0.0
type: software
abstract: "Machine-readable definitions of the European Genome-phenome Archive (EGA) and its Federation (FEGA) metadata model, together with examples, validation utilities, and documentation."
license: MIT
repository-code: "https://github.com/EGA-archive/fega-metadata-schema"
url: "https://github.com/EGA-archive/fega-metadata-schema"
keywords:
  - "EGA"
  - "FEGA"
  - "metadata"
  - "metadata model"
  - "JSON Schema"
  - "JSON-LD"
  - "FAIR"

